headline: Jacobs Secures Environmental Services Contract with US Air Force
summary: Jacobs (NYSE: J) was selected by the U.S. Air Force Civil Engineer Center (AFCEC) to deliver architecture and engineering globally through an indefinite delivery indefinite quantity (IDIQ), multiple award task order contract (MATOC) to support environmental restoration, environmental conservation, planning and environmental quality.
